{"ja443:0.1":"Jataka ","ja443:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja443:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja443:0.4":"5. Culabodhijataka ","ja443:1.1":"“Yo te imam visalakkhim, ","ja443:1.2":"piyam sammhitabhasinim; ","ja443:1.3":"Adaya bala gaccheyya, ","ja443:1.4":"kim nu kayirasi brahmana”. ","ja443:2.1":"“Uppajje me na mucceyya, ","ja443:2.2":"na me mucceyya jivato; ","ja443:2.3":"Rajamva vipula vutthi, ","ja443:2.4":"khippameva nivaraye”. ","ja443:3.1":"“Yannu pubbe vikatthittho, ","ja443:3.2":"balamhiva apassito; ","ja443:3.3":"Svajja tunhikato dani, ","ja443:3.4":"sanghatim sibbamacchasi”. ","ja443:4.1":"“Uppajji me na muccittha, ","ja443:4.2":"na me muccittha jivato; ","ja443:4.3":"Rajamva vipula vutthi, ","ja443:4.4":"khippameva nivarayim”. ","ja443:5.1":"“Kim te uppajji no mucci, ","ja443:5.2":"kim te na mucci jivato; ","ja443:5.3":"Rajamva vipula vutthi, ","ja443:5.4":"katamam tvam nivarayi”. ","ja443:6.1":"“Yamhi jate na passati, ","ja443:6.2":"ajate sadhu passati; ","ja443:6.3":"So me uppajji no mucci, ","ja443:6.4":"kodho dummedhagocaro. ","ja443:7.1":"Yena jatena nandanti, ","ja443:7.2":"amitta dukkhamesino; ","ja443:7.3":"So me uppajji no mucci, ","ja443:7.4":"kodho dummedhagocaro. ","ja443:8.1":"Yasminca jayamanamhi, ","ja443:8.2":"sadattham navabujjhati; ","ja443:8.3":"So me uppajji no mucci, ","ja443:8.4":"kodho dummedhagocaro. ","ja443:9.1":"Yenabhibhuto kusalam jahati, ","ja443:9.2":"Parakkare vipulancapi attham; ","ja443:9.3":"Sa bhimaseno balava pamaddi, ","ja443:9.4":"Kodho maharaja na me amuccatha. ","ja443:10.1":"Katthasmim matthamanasmim, ","ja443:10.2":"Pavako nama jayati; ","ja443:10.3":"Tameva kattham dahati, ","ja443:10.4":"Yasma so jayate gini. ","ja443:11.1":"Evam mandassa posassa, ","ja443:11.2":"balassa avijanato; ","ja443:11.3":"Sarambha jayate kodho, ","ja443:11.4":"sopi teneva dayhati. ","ja443:12.1":"Aggiva tinakatthasmim, ","ja443:12.2":"kodho yassa pavaddhati; ","ja443:12.3":"Nihiyati tassa yaso, ","ja443:12.4":"kalapakkheva candima. ","ja443:13.1":"Anedho dhumaketuva, ","ja443:13.2":"kodho yassupasammati; ","ja443:13.3":"Apurati tassa yaso, ","ja443:13.4":"sukkapakkheva candima”ti. ","ja443:14.1":"Culabodhijatakam pancamam. "}